<br>
As far as choosing faction based on your guild, I'm a 56th Dwarf Pally and the highest member of my guild, next highest is a few 53's.  Mostly a mid-level guild with 12 or so higher people around levle 50.  <br>
<br>
BUT, on the Tunare server, we have several large guilds.<br>
<br>
Talisman (giant ally, last time I saw Abs in mostly/full Shining)<br>
Pia Fidelis <br>
Vae Inimicus<br>
Primordium (dragon ally)<br>
Tide<br>
<br>
pardon me if I forgot one and I don't know what the other three guilds are ally to.<br>
<br>
Generally nice people :)   So I had the option of picking the faction I wanted.  I used to be guilded with most of the members of Primordium before Uprising disbanded so they don't mind me on their raids and they're mostly great people despite the Tunare Flames area.<br>
<br>
So basically, my guild, Rain of Steel, is just a bunch of friends, not a raiding guild.  We pick what faction we want.  Our highest magician, Maphesto is indiff to dragons and rising, and methinks our highest shaman, Mawg, is about the same to all the giants.<br>
<br>
One day we might actually become quite powerful.  <br>
